included.description:
Web Design & Programming course is a mandatory course for semester 3 students at Faculty of Computer Science Universitas Indonesia. It provides basic but end-to-end, industry-ready knowledge on web design and programming ranging from:
- Mockup and prototyping
- Create, read, update, and delete object on models
- Sessions and cookie
- Unit test and functional test
- Continuous integration pipeline
- Basic web service and OAuth
- Basic jQuery
The course were done by using Django Framework, Gitlab's continuous integration, and Heroku deployment. My responsibilities as a teaching assistant are grading, providing students with weekly challenges, providing personal assist and held tutorials and demo sessions.
included.title: Teaching Assistant - Web Design & Programming Course
